 INSERT INTO civicrm_line_item (entity_table , entity_id , contribution_id , price_field_id , label , qty , unit_price , line_total , price_field_value_id , financial_type_id ) VALUES ('civicrm_contribution' ,  46 ,  46 ,  1 , 'Contribution Amount' ,  1 ,  100 ,  100 ,  1 ,  1 ) 

 SELECT * 
 FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_table  = 'civicrm_financial_type' )  AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_id = 1 ) AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.account_relationship = 1 ) 
 
 
 


 SELECT ceft.id, ceft.financial_trxn_id FROM `civicrm_financial_trxn` cft
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft
ON ceft.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_contribution'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft1
ON ceft1.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_financial_item cfi ON ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item' and cfi.id = ceft1.entity_id
WHERE ceft.entity_id = 46 AND (cfi.entity_table <> 'civicrm_financial_trxn' or cfi.entity_table is NULL)

ORDER BY cft.id ASC
LIMIT 1;

 WHERE (  civicrm_activity.source_record_id = 48 )  AND (  civicrm_activity.activity_type_id = 6 ) 
 
 
 


 
SELECT  v.label as label ,v.value as value
FROM   civicrm_option_value v,
       civicrm_option_group g
WHERE  v.option_group_id = g.id
  AND  g.name            = 'activity_type'
  AND  v.is_active       = 1
  AND  g.is_active       = 1
  AND  v.name     = 'Contribution'


 
SELECT  v.label as label ,v.value as value
FROM   civicrm_option_value v,
       civicrm_option_group g
WHERE  v.option_group_id = g.id
  AND  g.name            = 'activity_status'
  AND  v.is_active       = 1
  AND  g.is_active       = 1
  AND  v.name     = 'Completed'


 INSERT INTO civicrm_activity (source_record_id , activity_type_id , subject , activity_date_time , status_id , priority_id ) VALUES ( 48 ,  6 , '$ 100.00 - SSF' ,  20120511000000 ,  2 ,  2 ) 

 SELECT * 
 FROM civicrm_activity_contact 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_activity_contact.activity_id = 48 )  AND (  civicrm_activity_contact.record_type_id = 2 ) 
 
 
 


 SELECT * 
 FROM civicrm_activity_contact 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_activity_contact.activity_id = 48 )  AND (  civicrm_activity_contact.contact_id = 3 ) AND (  civicrm_activity_contact.record_type_id = 2 ) 
 
 
 


 INSERT INTO civicrm_activity_contact (activity_id , contact_id , record_type_id ) VALUES ( 48 ,  3 ,  2 ) 

 SELECT * 
 FROM civicrm_activity_contact 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_activity_contact.activity_id = 48 )  AND (  civicrm_activity_contact.record_type_id = 1 ) 
 
 
 


 SELECT * 
 FROM civicrm_activity_contact 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_activity_contact.activity_id = 48 )  AND (  civicrm_activity_contact.record_type_id = 3 ) 
 
 
 


 SELECT * 
 FROM civicrm_activity_contact 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_activity_contact.activity_id = 48 )  AND (  civicrm_activity_contact.record_type_id = 2 ) 
 
 
 


 INSERT INTO civicrm_log (entity_table , entity_id , data , modified_id , modified_date ) VALUES ('civicrm_activity' ,  48 , 'Activity created for source=3' ,  3 ,  20151201183525 ) 

 COMMIT

 BEGIN

 
SELECT  v.label as label ,v.value as value
FROM   civicrm_option_value v,
       civicrm_option_group g
WHERE  v.option_group_id = g.id
  AND  g.name            = 'contribution_status'
  AND  v.is_active       = 1
  AND  g.is_active       = 1
  AND  v.name     = 'Completed'


 INSERT INTO civicrm_contribution (contact_id , financial_type_id , payment_instrument_id , receive_date , non_deductible_amount , total_amount , fee_amount , net_amount , currency , source , contribution_status_id ) VALUES ( 3 ,  1 ,  4 ,  20120511000000 ,  10 ,  100 ,  5 ,  95 , 'USD' , 'SSF' ,  1 ) 

 SELECT ceft.financial_account_id, cov.value
FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account ceft
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_value cov ON cov.id = ceft.entity_id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_option_value'
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_group cog ON cog.id = cov.option_group_id
WHERE cog.name = 'payment_instrument'  AND cov.value = '4' 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_financial_trxn (to_financial_account_id , trxn_date , total_amount , fee_amount , net_amount , currency , status_id , payment_instrument_id ) VALUES ( 6 ,  20120511000000 ,  100 ,  5 ,  95 , 'USD' ,  1 ,  4 ) 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_entity_financial_trxn (entity_table , entity_id , financial_trxn_id , amount ) VALUES ('civicrm_contribution' ,  49 ,  97 ,  100 ) 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_line_item (entity_table , entity_id , contribution_id , price_field_id , label , qty , unit_price , line_total , price_field_value_id , financial_type_id ) VALUES ('civicrm_contribution' ,  49 ,  49 ,  1 , 'Contribution Amount' ,  1 ,  100 ,  100 ,  1 ,  1 ) 

 SELECT * 
 FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_table  = 'civicrm_financial_type' )  AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_id = 1 ) AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.account_relationship = 1 ) 
 
 
 


 SELECT ceft.id, ceft.financial_trxn_id FROM `civicrm_financial_trxn` cft
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft
ON ceft.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_contribution'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft1
ON ceft1.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_financial_item cfi ON ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item' and cfi.id = ceft1.entity_id
WHERE ceft.entity_id = 49 AND (cfi.entity_table <> 'civicrm_financial_trxn' or cfi.entity_table is NULL)

ORDER BY cft.id ASC
LIMIT 1;

 INSERT INTO civicrm_financial_item (transaction_date , contact_id , description , amount , currency , financial_account_id , status_id , entity_table , entity_id ) VALUES ( 20120511000000 ,  3 , ' Contribution Amount' ,  100 , 'USD' ,  1 ,  1 , 'civicrm_line_item' ,  49 ) 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_entity_financial_trxn (entity_table , entity_id , financial_trxn_id , amount ) VALUES ('civicrm_financial_item' ,  97 ,  97 ,  100 )

 FROM civicrm_activity_contact 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_activity_contact.activity_id = 51 )  AND (  civicrm_activity_contact.record_type_id = 2 ) 
 
 
 


 INSERT INTO civicrm_log (entity_table , entity_id , data , modified_id , modified_date ) VALUES ('civicrm_activity' ,  51 , 'Activity created for source=3' ,  3 ,  20151201183526 ) 

 COMMIT

 BEGIN

 
SELECT  v.label as label ,v.value as value
FROM   civicrm_option_value v,
       civicrm_option_group g
WHERE  v.option_group_id = g.id
  AND  g.name            = 'contribution_status'
  AND  v.is_active       = 1
  AND  g.is_active       = 1
  AND  v.name     = 'Completed'


 INSERT INTO civicrm_contribution (contact_id , financial_type_id , payment_instrument_id , receive_date , non_deductible_amount , total_amount , fee_amount , net_amount , currency , source , contribution_status_id ) VALUES ( 3 ,  1 ,  4 ,  20120511000000 ,  10 ,  100 ,  5 ,  95 , 'USD' , 'SSF' ,  1 ) 

 SELECT ceft.financial_account_id, cov.value
FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account ceft
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_value cov ON cov.id = ceft.entity_id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_option_value'
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_group cog ON cog.id = cov.option_group_id
WHERE cog.name = 'payment_instrument'  AND cov.value = '4' 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_financial_trxn (to_financial_account_id , trxn_date , total_amount , fee_amount , net_amount , currency , status_id , payment_instrument_id ) VALUES ( 6 ,  20120511000000 ,  100 ,  5 ,  95 , 'USD' ,  1 ,  4 ) 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_entity_financial_trxn (entity_table , entity_id , financial_trxn_id , amount ) VALUES ('civicrm_contribution' ,  52 ,  103 ,  100 ) 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_line_item (entity_table , entity_id , contribution_id , price_field_id , label , qty , unit_price , line_total , price_field_value_id , financial_type_id ) VALUES ('civicrm_contribution' ,  52 ,  52 ,  1 , 'Contribution Amount' ,  1 ,  100 ,  100 ,  1 ,  1 ) 

 SELECT * 
 FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_table  = 'civicrm_financial_type' )  AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_id = 1 ) AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.account_relationship = 1 ) 
 
 
 


 SELECT ceft.id, ceft.financial_trxn_id FROM `civicrm_financial_trxn` cft
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft
ON ceft.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_contribution'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft1
ON ceft1.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_financial_item cfi ON ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item' and cfi.id = ceft1.entity_id
WHERE ceft.entity_id = 52 AND (cfi.entity_table <> 'civicrm_financial_trxn' or cfi.entity_table is NULL)

ORDER BY cft.id ASC
LIMIT 1;

 INSERT INTO civicrm_financial_item (transaction_date , contact_id , description , amount , currency , financial_account_id , status_id , entity_table , entity_id ) VALUES ( 20120511000000 ,  3 , ' Contribution Amount' ,  100 , 'USD' ,  1 ,  1 , 'civicrm_line_item' ,  52 ) 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_entity_financial_trxn (entity_table , entity_id , financial_trxn_id , amount ) VALUES ('civicrm_financial_item' ,  103 ,  103 ,  100 ) 

 
SELECT  v.label as label ,v.value as value
FROM   civicrm_option_value v,
       civicrm_option_group g
WHERE  v.option_group_id = g.id
  AND  g.name            = 'contribution_status'
  AND  v.is_active       = 1
  AND  g.is_active       = 1
  AND  v.name     = 'Completed'

 INSERT INTO civicrm_line_item (entity_table , entity_id , contribution_id , price_field_id , label , qty , unit_price , line_total , price_field_value_id , financial_type_id ) VALUES ('civicrm_contribution' ,  55 ,  55 ,  1 , 'Contribution Amount' ,  1 ,  100 ,  100 ,  1 ,  1 ) 

 SELECT * 
 FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_table  = 'civicrm_financial_type' )  AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_id = 1 ) AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.account_relationship = 1 ) 
 
 
 


 SELECT ceft.id, ceft.financial_trxn_id FROM `civicrm_financial_trxn` cft
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft
ON ceft.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_contribution'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft1
ON ceft1.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_financial_item cfi ON ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item' and cfi.id = ceft1.entity_id
WHERE ceft.entity_id = 55 AND (cfi.entity_table <> 'civicrm_financial_trxn' or cfi.entity_table is NULL)

ORDER BY cft.id ASC
LIMIT 1;

 INSERT INTO civicrm_financial_item (transaction_date , contact_id , description , amount , currency , financial_account_id , status_id , entity_table , entity_id ) VALUES ( 20120511000000 ,  3 , ' Contribution Amount' ,  100 , 'USD' ,  1 ,  1 , 'civicrm_line_item' ,  55 ) 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_entity_financial_trxn (entity_table , entity_id , financial_trxn_id , amount ) VALUES ('civicrm_financial_item' ,  109 ,  109 ,  100 ) 

 
SELECT  v.label as label ,v.value as value
FROM   civicrm_option_value v,
       civicrm_option_group g
WHERE  v.option_group_id = g.id
  AND  g.name            = 'contribution_status'
  AND  v.is_active       = 1
  AND  g.is_active       = 1
  AND  v.name     = 'Completed'

  AND  v.name     = 'Paid'

 SELECT ceft.financial_account_id, cov.value
FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account ceft
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_value cov ON cov.id = ceft.entity_id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_option_value'
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_group cog ON cog.id = cov.option_group_id
WHERE cog.name = 'payment_instrument'  AND cov.value = '4'

 INSERT INTO civicrm_contribution (contact_id , financial_type_id , payment_instrument_id , receive_date , non_deductible_amount , total_amount , fee_amount , net_amount , currency , source , contribution_status_id ) VALUES ( 3 ,  1 ,  4 ,  20120511000000 ,  10 ,  100 ,  5 ,  95 , 'USD' , 'SSF' ,  1 ) 

 SELECT ceft.financial_account_id, cov.value
FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account ceft
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_value cov ON cov.id = ceft.entity_id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_option_value'
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_group cog ON cog.id = cov.option_group_id
WHERE cog.name = 'payment_instrument'  AND cov.value = '4' 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_financial_trxn (to_financial_account_id , trxn_date , total_amount , fee_amount , net_amount , currency , status_id , payment_instrument_id ) VALUES ( 6 ,  20120511000000 ,  100 ,  5 ,  95 , 'USD' ,  1 ,  4 ) 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_entity_financial_trxn (entity_table , entity_id , financial_trxn_id , amount ) VALUES ('civicrm_contribution' ,  59 ,  117 ,  100 ) 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_line_item (entity_table , entity_id , contribution_id , price_field_id , label , qty , unit_price , line_total , price_field_value_id , financial_type_id ) VALUES ('civicrm_contribution' ,  59 ,  59 ,  1 , 'Contribution Amount' ,  1 ,  100 ,  100 ,  1 ,  1 ) 

 SELECT * 
 FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_table  = 'civicrm_financial_type' )  AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_id = 1 ) AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.account_relationship = 1 ) 
 
 
 


 SELECT ceft.id, ceft.financial_trxn_id FROM `civicrm_financial_trxn` cft
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft
ON ceft.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_contribution'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft1
ON ceft1.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_financial_item cfi ON ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item' and cfi.id = ceft1.entity_id
WHERE ceft.entity_id = 59 AND (cfi.entity_table <> 'civicrm_financial_trxn' or cfi.entity_table is NULL)

ORDER BY cft.id ASC
LIMIT 1;

 SELECT ceft.financial_account_id, cov.value
FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account ceft
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_value cov ON cov.id = ceft.entity_id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_option_value'
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_group cog ON cog.id = cov.option_group_id
WHERE cog.name = 'payment_instrument'  AND cov.value = '4' 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_financial_trxn (to_financial_account_id , trxn_date , total_amount , fee_amount , net_amount , currency , status_id , payment_instrument_id ) VALUES ( 6 ,  20120511000000 ,  100 ,  5 ,  95 , 'USD' ,  1 ,  4 )

 INSERT INTO civicrm_line_item (entity_table , entity_id , contribution_id , price_field_id , label , qty , unit_price , line_total , price_field_value_id , financial_type_id ) VALUES ('civicrm_contribution' ,  62 ,  62 ,  1 , 'Contribution Amount' ,  1 ,  100 ,  100 ,  1 ,  1 ) 

 SELECT * 
 FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_table  = 'civicrm_financial_type' )  AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_id = 1 ) AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.account_relationship = 1 ) 
 
 
 


 SELECT ceft.id, ceft.financial_trxn_id FROM `civicrm_financial_trxn` cft
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft
ON ceft.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_contribution'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft1
ON ceft1.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_financial_item cfi ON ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item' and cfi.id = ceft1.entity_id
WHERE ceft.entity_id = 62 AND (cfi.entity_table <> 'civicrm_financial_trxn' or cfi.entity_table is NULL)

ORDER BY cft.id ASC
LIMIT 1;

 SELECT ceft.financial_account_id, cov.value
FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account ceft
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_value cov ON cov.id = ceft.entity_id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_option_value'
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_group cog ON cog.id = cov.option_group_id
WHERE cog.name = 'payment_instrument'  AND cov.value = '4' 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_financial_trxn (to_financial_account_id , trxn_date , total_amount , fee_amount , net_amount , currency , status_id , payment_instrument_id ) VALUES ( 6 ,  20120511000000 ,  100 ,  5 ,  95 , 'USD' ,  1 ,  4 ) 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_entity_financial_trxn (entity_table , entity_id , financial_trxn_id , amount ) VALUES ('civicrm_contribution' ,  65 ,  129 ,  100 ) 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_line_item (entity_table , entity_id , contribution_id , price_field_id , label , qty , unit_price , line_total , price_field_value_id , financial_type_id ) VALUES ('civicrm_contribution' ,  65 ,  65 ,  1 , 'Contribution Amount' ,  1 ,  100 ,  100 ,  1 ,  1 ) 

 SELECT * 
 FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_table  = 'civicrm_financial_type' )  AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_id = 1 ) AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.account_relationship = 1 ) 
 
 
 


 SELECT ceft.id, ceft.financial_trxn_id FROM `civicrm_financial_trxn` cft
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft
ON ceft.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_contribution'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft1
ON ceft1.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_financial_item cfi ON ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item' and cfi.id = ceft1.entity_id
WHERE ceft.entity_id = 65 AND (cfi.entity_table <> 'civicrm_financial_trxn' or cfi.entity_table is NULL)

ORDER BY cft.id ASC
LIMIT 1;

 SELECT ceft.financial_account_id, cov.value
FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account ceft
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_value cov ON cov.id = ceft.entity_id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_option_value'
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_group cog ON cog.id = cov.option_group_id
WHERE cog.name = 'payment_instrument'  AND cov.value = '4'

 SELECT * 
 FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_table  = 'civicrm_financial_type' )  AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_id = 1 ) AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.account_relationship = 1 ) 
 
 
 


 SELECT ceft.id, ceft.financial_trxn_id FROM `civicrm_financial_trxn` cft
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft
ON ceft.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_contribution'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft1
ON ceft1.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_financial_item cfi ON ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item' and cfi.id = ceft1.entity_id
WHERE ceft.entity_id = 68 AND (cfi.entity_table <> 'civicrm_financial_trxn' or cfi.entity_table is NULL)

ORDER BY cft.id ASC
LIMIT 1;

       civicrm_option_group g

  AND  g.name            = 'contribution_status'

  AND  g.is_active       = 1
  AND  v.name     = 'Completed'

 SELECT ceft.id, ceft.financial_trxn_id FROM `civicrm_financial_trxn` cft
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft
ON ceft.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_contribution'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft1
ON ceft1.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_financial_item cfi ON ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item' and cfi.id = ceft1.entity_id
WHERE ceft.entity_id = 71 AND (cfi.entity_table <> 'civicrm_financial_trxn' or cfi.entity_table is NULL)

ORDER BY cft.id ASC
LIMIT 1;

 INSERT INTO civicrm_financial_item (transaction_date , contact_id , description , amount , currency , financial_account_id , status_id , entity_table , entity_id ) VALUES ( 20120511000000 ,  3 , ' Contribution Amount' ,  100 , 'USD' ,  1 ,  1 , 'civicrm_line_item' ,  71 ) 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_entity_financial_trxn (entity_table , entity_id , financial_trxn_id , amount ) VALUES ('civicrm_financial_item' ,  141 ,  141 ,  100 ) 

 
SELECT  v.label as label ,v.value as value
FROM   civicrm_option_value v,
       civicrm_option_group g
WHERE  v.option_group_id = g.id
  AND  g.name            = 'contribution_status'
  AND  v.is_active       = 1
  AND  g.is_active       = 1
  AND  v.name     = 'Completed'


 INSERT INTO civicrm_financial_trxn (from_financial_account_id , to_financial_account_id , trxn_date , total_amount , fee_amount , net_amount , currency , status_id , payment_instrument_id ) VALUES ( 6 ,  5 ,  20120511000000 ,  5 ,  0 ,  0 , 'USD' ,  1 ,  4 ) 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_entity_financial_trxn (entity_table , entity_id , financial_trxn_id , amount ) VALUES ('civicrm_contribution' ,  71 ,  142 ,  5 ) 

 
SELECT  v.label as label ,v.value as value
FROM   civicrm_option_value v,
       civicrm_option_group g
WHERE  v.option_group_id = g.id
  AND  g.name            = 'financial_item_status'
  AND  v.is_active       = 1
  AND  g.is_active       = 1
  AND  v.name     = 'Paid'

       civicrm_option_group g
WHERE  v.option_group_id = g.id
  AND  g.name            = 'activity_type'
  AND  v.is_active       = 1
  AND  g.is_active       = 1
  AND  v.name     = 'Contribution'

 INSERT INTO civicrm_contribution (contact_id , financial_type_id , payment_instrument_id , receive_date , non_deductible_amount , total_amount , fee_amount , net_amount , currency , source , contribution_status_id ) VALUES ( 3 ,  1 ,  4 ,  20120511000000 ,  10 ,  100 ,  5 ,  95 , 'USD' , 'SSF' ,  1 ) 

 SELECT ceft.financial_account_id, cov.value
FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account ceft
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_value cov ON cov.id = ceft.entity_id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_option_value'
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_group cog ON cog.id = cov.option_group_id
WHERE cog.name = 'payment_instrument'  AND cov.value = '4' 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_financial_trxn (to_financial_account_id , trxn_date , total_amount , fee_amount , net_amount , currency , status_id , payment_instrument_id ) VALUES ( 6 ,  20120511000000 ,  100 ,  5 ,  95 , 'USD' ,  1 ,  4 )

 SELECT * 
 FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_table  = 'civicrm_financial_type' )  AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_id = 1 ) AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.account_relationship = 1 )

ON ceft.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_contribution'

WHERE ceft.entity_id = 72 AND (cfi.entity_table <> 'civicrm_financial_trxn' or cfi.entity_table is NULL)

ORDER BY cft.id ASC
LIMIT 1;

 SELECT ceft.financial_account_id, cov.value
FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account ceft
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_value cov ON cov.id = ceft.entity_id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_option_value'
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_group cog ON cog.id = cov.option_group_id
WHERE cog.name = 'payment_instrument'  AND cov.value = '4' 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_financial_trxn (to_financial_account_id , trxn_date , total_amount , fee_amount , net_amount , currency , status_id , payment_instrument_id ) VALUES ( 6 ,  20120511000000 ,  100 ,  5 ,  95 , 'USD' ,  1 ,  4 ) 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_entity_financial_trxn (entity_table , entity_id , financial_trxn_id , amount ) VALUES ('civicrm_contribution' ,  75 ,  149 ,  100 ) 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_line_item (entity_table , entity_id , contribution_id , price_field_id , label , qty , unit_price , line_total , price_field_value_id , financial_type_id ) VALUES ('civicrm_contribution' ,  75 ,  75 ,  1 , 'Contribution Amount' ,  1 ,  100 ,  100 ,  1 ,  1 ) 

 SELECT * 
 FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_table  = 'civicrm_financial_type' )  AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_id = 1 ) AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.account_relationship = 1 ) 
 
 
 


 SELECT ceft.id, ceft.financial_trxn_id FROM `civicrm_financial_trxn` cft
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft
ON ceft.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_contribution'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft1
ON ceft1.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_financial_item cfi ON ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item' and cfi.id = ceft1.entity_id
WHERE ceft.entity_id = 75 AND (cfi.entity_table <> 'civicrm_financial_trxn' or cfi.entity_table is NULL)

ORDER BY cft.id ASC
LIMIT 1;

 WHERE (  civicrm_activity.source_record_id = 77 )  AND (  civicrm_activity.activity_type_id = 6 ) 
 
 
 


 
SELECT  v.label as label ,v.value as value
FROM   civicrm_option_value v,
       civicrm_option_group g
WHERE  v.option_group_id = g.id
  AND  g.name            = 'activity_type'
  AND  v.is_active       = 1
  AND  g.is_active       = 1
  AND  v.name     = 'Contribution'


 
SELECT  v.label as label ,v.value as value
FROM   civicrm_option_value v,
       civicrm_option_group g
WHERE  v.option_group_id = g.id
  AND  g.name            = 'activity_status'
  AND  v.is_active       = 1
  AND  g.is_active       = 1
  AND  v.name     = 'Completed'


 INSERT INTO civicrm_activity (source_record_id , activity_type_id , subject , activity_date_time , status_id , priority_id ) VALUES ( 77 ,  6 , '$ 100.00 - SSF' ,  20120511000000 ,  2 ,  2 ) 

 SELECT * 
 FROM civicrm_activity_contact 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_activity_contact.activity_id = 77 )  AND (  civicrm_activity_contact.record_type_id = 2 ) 
 
 
 


 SELECT * 
 FROM civicrm_activity_contact 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_activity_contact.activity_id = 77 )  AND (  civicrm_activity_contact.contact_id = 3 ) AND (  civicrm_activity_contact.record_type_id = 2 ) 
 
 
 


 INSERT INTO civicrm_activity_contact (activity_id , contact_id , record_type_id ) VALUES ( 77 ,  3 ,  2 ) 

 SELECT * 
 FROM civicrm_activity_contact 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_activity_contact.activity_id = 77 )  AND (  civicrm_activity_contact.record_type_id = 1 ) 
 
 
 


 SELECT * 
 FROM civicrm_activity_contact 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_activity_contact.activity_id = 77 )  AND (  civicrm_activity_contact.record_type_id = 3 ) 
 
 
 


 SELECT * 
 FROM civicrm_activity_contact 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_activity_contact.activity_id = 77 )  AND (  civicrm_activity_contact.record_type_id = 2 ) 
 
 
 


 INSERT INTO civicrm_log (entity_table , entity_id , data , modified_id , modified_date ) VALUES ('civicrm_activity' ,  77 , 'Activity created for source=3' ,  3 ,  20151201183531 ) 

 COMMIT

 BEGIN

 
SELECT  v.label as label ,v.value as value
FROM   civicrm_option_value v,
       civicrm_option_group g
WHERE  v.option_group_id = g.id
  AND  g.name            = 'contribution_status'
  AND  v.is_active       = 1
  AND  g.is_active       = 1
  AND  v.name     = 'Completed'


 INSERT INTO civicrm_contribution (contact_id , financial_type_id , payment_instrument_id , receive_date , non_deductible_amount , total_amount , fee_amount , net_amount , currency , source , contribution_status_id ) VALUES ( 3 ,  1 ,  4 ,  20120511000000 ,  10 ,  100 ,  5 ,  95 , 'USD' , 'SSF' ,  1 ) 

 SELECT ceft.financial_account_id, cov.value
FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account ceft
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_value cov ON cov.id = ceft.entity_id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_option_value'
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_group cog ON cog.id = cov.option_group_id
WHERE cog.name = 'payment_instrument'  AND cov.value = '4' 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_financial_trxn (to_financial_account_id , trxn_date , total_amount , fee_amount , net_amount , currency , status_id , payment_instrument_id ) VALUES ( 6 ,  20120511000000 ,  100 ,  5 ,  95 , 'USD' ,  1 ,  4 ) 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_entity_financial_trxn (entity_table , entity_id , financial_trxn_id , amount ) VALUES ('civicrm_contribution' ,  78 ,  155 ,  100 ) 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_line_item (entity_table , entity_id , contribution_id , price_field_id , label , qty , unit_price , line_total , price_field_value_id , financial_type_id ) VALUES ('civicrm_contribution' ,  78 ,  78 ,  1 , 'Contribution Amount' ,  1 ,  100 ,  100 ,  1 ,  1 ) 

 SELECT * 
 FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_table  = 'civicrm_financial_type' )  AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_id = 1 ) AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.account_relationship = 1 ) 
 
 
 


 SELECT ceft.id, ceft.financial_trxn_id FROM `civicrm_financial_trxn` cft
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft
ON ceft.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_contribution'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft1
ON ceft1.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_financial_item cfi ON ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item' and cfi.id = ceft1.entity_id
WHERE ceft.entity_id = 78 AND (cfi.entity_table <> 'civicrm_financial_trxn' or cfi.entity_table is NULL)

ORDER BY cft.id ASC
LIMIT 1;

 INSERT INTO civicrm_financial_item (transaction_date , contact_id , description , amount , currency , financial_account_id , status_id , entity_table , entity_id ) VALUES ( 20120511000000 ,  3 , ' Contribution Amount' ,  100 , 'USD' ,  1 ,  1 , 'civicrm_line_item' ,  78 ) 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_entity_financial_trxn (entity_table , entity_id , financial_trxn_id , amount ) VALUES ('civicrm_financial_item' ,  155 ,  155 ,  100 )

  AND  g.name            = 'contribution_status'

  AND  v.name     = 'Completed'

 FROM civicrm_activity_contact 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_activity_contact.activity_id = 80 )  AND (  civicrm_activity_contact.record_type_id = 2 ) 
 
 
 


 INSERT INTO civicrm_log (entity_table , entity_id , data , modified_id , modified_date ) VALUES ('civicrm_activity' ,  80 , 'Activity created for source=3' ,  3 ,  20151201183531 ) 

 COMMIT

 BEGIN

 
SELECT  v.label as label ,v.value as value
FROM   civicrm_option_value v,
       civicrm_option_group g
WHERE  v.option_group_id = g.id
  AND  g.name            = 'contribution_status'
  AND  v.is_active       = 1
  AND  g.is_active       = 1
  AND  v.name     = 'Completed'


 INSERT INTO civicrm_contribution (contact_id , financial_type_id , payment_instrument_id , receive_date , non_deductible_amount , total_amount , fee_amount , net_amount , currency , source , contribution_status_id ) VALUES ( 3 ,  1 ,  4 ,  20120511000000 ,  10 ,  100 ,  5 ,  95 , 'USD' , 'SSF' ,  1 ) 

 SELECT ceft.financial_account_id, cov.value
FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account ceft
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_value cov ON cov.id = ceft.entity_id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_option_value'
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_group cog ON cog.id = cov.option_group_id
WHERE cog.name = 'payment_instrument'  AND cov.value = '4' 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_financial_trxn (to_financial_account_id , trxn_date , total_amount , fee_amount , net_amount , currency , status_id , payment_instrument_id ) VALUES ( 6 ,  20120511000000 ,  100 ,  5 ,  95 , 'USD' ,  1 ,  4 ) 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_entity_financial_trxn (entity_table , entity_id , financial_trxn_id , amount ) VALUES ('civicrm_contribution' ,  81 ,  161 ,  100 ) 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_line_item (entity_table , entity_id , contribution_id , price_field_id , label , qty , unit_price , line_total , price_field_value_id , financial_type_id ) VALUES ('civicrm_contribution' ,  81 ,  81 ,  1 , 'Contribution Amount' ,  1 ,  100 ,  100 ,  1 ,  1 ) 

 SELECT * 
 FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_table  = 'civicrm_financial_type' )  AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_id = 1 ) AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.account_relationship = 1 ) 
 
 
 


 SELECT ceft.id, ceft.financial_trxn_id FROM `civicrm_financial_trxn` cft
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft
ON ceft.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_contribution'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft1
ON ceft1.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_financial_item cfi ON ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item' and cfi.id = ceft1.entity_id
WHERE ceft.entity_id = 81 AND (cfi.entity_table <> 'civicrm_financial_trxn' or cfi.entity_table is NULL)

ORDER BY cft.id ASC
LIMIT 1;

 INSERT INTO civicrm_financial_item (transaction_date , contact_id , description , amount , currency , financial_account_id , status_id , entity_table , entity_id ) VALUES ( 20120511000000 ,  3 , ' Contribution Amount' ,  100 , 'USD' ,  1 ,  1 , 'civicrm_line_item' ,  81 ) 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_entity_financial_trxn (entity_table , entity_id , financial_trxn_id , amount ) VALUES ('civicrm_financial_item' ,  161 ,  161 ,  100 ) 

 
SELECT  v.label as label ,v.value as value
FROM   civicrm_option_value v,
       civicrm_option_group g
WHERE  v.option_group_id = g.id
  AND  g.name            = 'contribution_status'
  AND  v.is_active       = 1
  AND  g.is_active       = 1
  AND  v.name     = 'Completed'

 INSERT INTO civicrm_line_item (entity_table , entity_id , contribution_id , price_field_id , label , qty , unit_price , line_total , price_field_value_id , financial_type_id ) VALUES ('civicrm_contribution' ,  84 ,  84 ,  1 , 'Contribution Amount' ,  1 ,  100 ,  100 ,  1 ,  1 ) 

 SELECT * 
 FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_table  = 'civicrm_financial_type' )  AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_id = 1 ) AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.account_relationship = 1 ) 
 
 
 


 SELECT ceft.id, ceft.financial_trxn_id FROM `civicrm_financial_trxn` cft
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft
ON ceft.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_contribution'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft1
ON ceft1.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_financial_item cfi ON ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item' and cfi.id = ceft1.entity_id
WHERE ceft.entity_id = 84 AND (cfi.entity_table <> 'civicrm_financial_trxn' or cfi.entity_table is NULL)

ORDER BY cft.id ASC
LIMIT 1;

 INSERT INTO civicrm_financial_item (transaction_date , contact_id , description , amount , currency , financial_account_id , status_id , entity_table , entity_id ) VALUES ( 20120511000000 ,  3 , ' Contribution Amount' ,  100 , 'USD' ,  1 ,  1 , 'civicrm_line_item' ,  84 ) 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_entity_financial_trxn (entity_table , entity_id , financial_trxn_id , amount ) VALUES ('civicrm_financial_item' ,  167 ,  167 ,  100 ) 

 
SELECT  v.label as label ,v.value as value
FROM   civicrm_option_value v,
       civicrm_option_group g
WHERE  v.option_group_id = g.id
  AND  g.name            = 'contribution_status'
  AND  v.is_active       = 1
  AND  g.is_active       = 1
  AND  v.name     = 'Completed'

 SELECT ceft.financial_account_id, cov.value
FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account ceft
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_value cov ON cov.id = ceft.entity_id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_option_value'
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_group cog ON cog.id = cov.option_group_id
WHERE cog.name = 'payment_instrument'  AND cov.value = '4'

 INSERT INTO civicrm_contribution (contact_id , financial_type_id , payment_instrument_id , receive_date , non_deductible_amount , total_amount , fee_amount , net_amount , currency , source , contribution_status_id ) VALUES ( 3 ,  1 ,  4 ,  20120511000000 ,  10 ,  100 ,  5 ,  95 , 'USD' , 'SSF' ,  1 ) 

 SELECT ceft.financial_account_id, cov.value
FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account ceft
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_value cov ON cov.id = ceft.entity_id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_option_value'
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_group cog ON cog.id = cov.option_group_id
WHERE cog.name = 'payment_instrument'  AND cov.value = '4' 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_financial_trxn (to_financial_account_id , trxn_date , total_amount , fee_amount , net_amount , currency , status_id , payment_instrument_id ) VALUES ( 6 ,  20120511000000 ,  100 ,  5 ,  95 , 'USD' ,  1 ,  4 ) 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_entity_financial_trxn (entity_table , entity_id , financial_trxn_id , amount ) VALUES ('civicrm_contribution' ,  88 ,  175 ,  100 ) 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_line_item (entity_table , entity_id , contribution_id , price_field_id , label , qty , unit_price , line_total , price_field_value_id , financial_type_id ) VALUES ('civicrm_contribution' ,  88 ,  88 ,  1 , 'Contribution Amount' ,  1 ,  100 ,  100 ,  1 ,  1 ) 

 SELECT * 
 FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_table  = 'civicrm_financial_type' )  AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_id = 1 ) AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.account_relationship = 1 ) 
 
 
 


 SELECT ceft.id, ceft.financial_trxn_id FROM `civicrm_financial_trxn` cft
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft
ON ceft.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_contribution'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft1
ON ceft1.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_financial_item cfi ON ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item' and cfi.id = ceft1.entity_id
WHERE ceft.entity_id = 88 AND (cfi.entity_table <> 'civicrm_financial_trxn' or cfi.entity_table is NULL)

ORDER BY cft.id ASC
LIMIT 1;

 SELECT ceft.financial_account_id, cov.value
FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account ceft
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_value cov ON cov.id = ceft.entity_id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_option_value'
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_group cog ON cog.id = cov.option_group_id
WHERE cog.name = 'payment_instrument'  AND cov.value = '4' 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_financial_trxn (to_financial_account_id , trxn_date , total_amount , fee_amount , net_amount , currency , status_id , payment_instrument_id ) VALUES ( 6 ,  20120511000000 ,  100 ,  5 ,  95 , 'USD' ,  1 ,  4 )

 INSERT INTO civicrm_line_item (entity_table , entity_id , contribution_id , price_field_id , label , qty , unit_price , line_total , price_field_value_id , financial_type_id ) VALUES ('civicrm_contribution' ,  91 ,  91 ,  1 , 'Contribution Amount' ,  1 ,  100 ,  100 ,  1 ,  1 ) 

 SELECT * 
 FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_table  = 'civicrm_financial_type' )  AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_id = 1 ) AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.account_relationship = 1 ) 
 
 
 


 SELECT ceft.id, ceft.financial_trxn_id FROM `civicrm_financial_trxn` cft
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft
ON ceft.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_contribution'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft1
ON ceft1.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_financial_item cfi ON ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item' and cfi.id = ceft1.entity_id
WHERE ceft.entity_id = 91 AND (cfi.entity_table <> 'civicrm_financial_trxn' or cfi.entity_table is NULL)

ORDER BY cft.id ASC
LIMIT 1;

 SELECT ceft.financial_account_id, cov.value
FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account ceft
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_value cov ON cov.id = ceft.entity_id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_option_value'
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_group cog ON cog.id = cov.option_group_id
WHERE cog.name = 'payment_instrument'  AND cov.value = '4' 

 INSERT INTO civicrm_financial_trxn (to_financial_account_id , trxn_date , total_amount , fee_amount , net_amount , currency , status_id , payment_instrument_id ) VALUES ( 6 ,  20120511000000 ,  100 ,  5 ,  95 , 'USD' ,  1 ,  4 )

 INSERT INTO civicrm_line_item (entity_table , entity_id , contribution_id , price_field_id , label , qty , unit_price , line_total , price_field_value_id , financial_type_id ) VALUES ('civicrm_contribution' ,  94 ,  94 ,  1 , 'Contribution Amount' ,  1 ,  100 ,  100 ,  1 ,  1 ) 

 SELECT * 
 FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_table  = 'civicrm_financial_type' )  AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_id = 1 ) AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.account_relationship = 1 ) 
 
 
 


 SELECT ceft.id, ceft.financial_trxn_id FROM `civicrm_financial_trxn` cft
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft
ON ceft.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_contribution'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft1
ON ceft1.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_financial_item cfi ON ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item' and cfi.id = ceft1.entity_id
WHERE ceft.entity_id = 94 AND (cfi.entity_table <> 'civicrm_financial_trxn' or cfi.entity_table is NULL)

ORDER BY cft.id ASC
LIMIT 1;

 SELECT ceft.financial_account_id, cov.value
FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account ceft
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_value cov ON cov.id = ceft.entity_id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_option_value'
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_group cog ON cog.id = cov.option_group_id
WHERE cog.name = 'payment_instrument'  AND cov.value = '4'

 INSERT INTO civicrm_line_item (entity_table , entity_id , contribution_id , price_field_id , label , qty , unit_price , line_total , price_field_value_id , financial_type_id ) VALUES ('civicrm_contribution' ,  97 ,  97 ,  1 , 'Contribution Amount' ,  1 ,  100 ,  100 ,  1 ,  1 ) 

 SELECT * 
 FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account 
 
 WHERE (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_table  = 'civicrm_financial_type' )  AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.entity_id = 1 ) AND (  civicrm_entity_financial_account.account_relationship = 1 ) 
 
 
 


 SELECT ceft.id, ceft.financial_trxn_id FROM `civicrm_financial_trxn` cft
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft
ON ceft.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_contribution'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft1
ON ceft1.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_financial_item cfi ON ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item' and cfi.id = ceft1.entity_id
WHERE ceft.entity_id = 97 AND (cfi.entity_table <> 'civicrm_financial_trxn' or cfi.entity_table is NULL)

ORDER BY cft.id ASC
LIMIT 1;

FROM   civicrm_option_value v,
       civicrm_option_group g
WHERE  v.option_group_id = g.id
  AND  g.name            = 'contribution_status'
  AND  v.is_active       = 1
  AND  g.is_active       = 1
  AND  v.name     = 'Completed'

LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft
ON ceft.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_contribution'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_entity_financial_trxn ceft1
ON ceft1.financial_trxn_id = cft.id AND ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item'
LEFT JOIN civicrm_financial_item cfi ON ceft1.entity_table = 'civicrm_financial_item' and cfi.id = ceft1.entity_id
WHERE ceft.entity_id = 100 AND (cfi.entity_table <> 'civicrm_financial_trxn' or cfi.entity_table is NULL)

ORDER BY cft.id ASC
LIMIT 1;

 SELECT ceft.financial_account_id, cov.value
FROM civicrm_entity_financial_account ceft
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_value cov ON cov.id = ceft.entity_id AND ceft.entity_table = 'civicrm_option_value'
INNER JOIN civicrm_option_group cog ON cog.id = cov.option_group_id
WHERE cog.name = 'payment_instrument'  AND cov.value = '4'

 FROM civicrm_cache

 SELECT id AS id, name AS label FROM civicrm_domain ORDER BY name

 
SELECT f.id, f.label, f.data_type,
       f.html_type, f.is_search_range,
       f.option_group_id, f.custom_group_id,
       f.column_name, g.table_name,
       f.date_format,f.time_format
  FROM civicrm_custom_field f
  JOIN civicrm_custom_group g ON f.custom_group_id = g.id
 WHERE g.is_active = 1
   AND f.is_active = 1
   AND g.extends = 'PaymentProcessor'

 SELECT a.id as id, a.domain_id as domain_id, a.name as name, a.description as description, a.payment_processor_type_id as payment_processor_type_id, a.is_active as is_active, a.is_default as is_default, a.is_test as is_test, a.user_name as user_name, a.password as password, a.signature as signature, a.url_site as url_site, a.url_api as url_api, a.url_recur as url_recur, a.url_button as url_button, a.subject as subject, a.class_name as class_name, a.billing_mode as billing_mode, a.is_recur as is_recur, a.payment_type as payment_type, a.payment_instrument_id as payment_instrument_id
FROM civicrm_payment_processor a
WHERE (a.is_active = "1") AND (a.domain_id = "1")
ORDER BY is_default DESC
LIMIT 25
OFFSET 0


 
SELECT  v.label as label ,v.value as value
FROM   civicrm_option_value v,
       civicrm_option_group g
WHERE  v.option_group_id = g.id
  AND  g.name            = 'payment_instrument'
  AND  v.is_active       = 1
  AND  g.is_active       = 1
  AND  v.name     = 'Check'


 
SELECT f.id, f.label, f.data_type,
       f.html_type, f.is_search_range,
       f.option_group_id, f.custom_group_id,
       f.column_name, g.table_name,
       f.date_format,f.time_format
  FROM civicrm_custom_field f
  JOIN civicrm_custom_group g ON f.custom_group_id = g.id
 WHERE g.is_active = 1
   AND f.is_active = 1
   AND g.extends = 'PaymentProcessor'

 SELECT a.id as id, a.domain_id as domain_id, a.name as name, a.description as description, a.payment_processor_type_id as payment_processor_type_id, a.is_active as is_active, a.is_default as is_default, a.is_test as is_test, a.user_name as user_name, a.password as password, a.signature as signature, a.url_site as url_site, a.url_api as url_api, a.url_recur as url_recur, a.url_button as url_button, a.subject as subject, a.class_name as class_name, a.billing_mode as billing_mode, a.is_recur as is_recur, a.payment_type as payment_type, a.payment_instrument_id as payment_instrument_id
FROM civicrm_payment_processor a
WHERE (a.is_active = "1") AND (a.domain_id = "1") AND (a.is_test = "0")
ORDER BY is_default DESC
LIMIT 25
OFFSET 0


 
SELECT  v.label as label ,v.value as value
FROM   civicrm_option_value v,
       civicrm_option_group g
WHERE  v.option_group_id = g.id
  AND  g.name            = 'payment_instrument'
  AND  v.is_active       = 1
  AND  g.is_active       = 1
  AND  v.name     = 'Check'


 
SELECT f.id, f.label, f.data_type,
       f.html_type, f.is_search_range,
       f.option_group_id, f.custom_group_id,
       f.column_name, g.table_name,
       f.date_format,f.time_format
  FROM civicrm_custom_field f
  JOIN civicrm_custom_group g ON f.custom_group_id = g.id
 WHERE g.is_active = 1
   AND f.is_active = 1
   AND g.extends = 'PaymentProcessor'

 SELECT a.id as id, a.domain_id as domain_id, a.name as name, a.description as description, a.payment_processor_type_id as payment_processor_type_id, a.is_active as is_active, a.is_default as is_default, a.is_test as is_test, a.user_name as user_name, a.password as password, a.signature as signature, a.url_site as url_site, a.url_api as url_api, a.url_recur as url_recur, a.url_button as url_button, a.subject as subject, a.class_name as class_name, a.billing_mode as billing_mode, a.is_recur as is_recur, a.payment_type as payment_type, a.payment_instrument_id as payment_instrument_id
FROM civicrm_payment_processor a
WHERE (a.is_active = "1") AND (a.domain_id = "1") AND (a.is_test = "1")
ORDER BY is_default DESC
LIMIT 25
OFFSET 0


 
SELECT  v.label as label ,v.value as value
FROM   civicrm_option_value v,
       civicrm_option_group g
WHERE  v.option_group_id = g.id
  AND  g.name            = 'payment_instrument'
  AND  v.is_active       = 1
  AND  g.is_active       = 1
  AND  v.name     = 'Check'
